Homelab

Proxmox VE homelab running on Intel Xeon E3-1230 V2.

Services:
- Home Assistant (VM 100) - Smart home automation
- Nextcloud - Self-hosted cloud storage 
- Vaultwarden - Password manager
	-> external access: Tailscale (Free Simple) or WireGuard

Custom Projects:
- Voice-activated Hue lighting
- Calendar -> WiiM Ultra -> Power Amplifier standby Trigger -> 5s -> audio reminders
- Siri integration
- Possible cheap AliSexpress microphone voice activation integration

